  displayName: The Digital Uprising Wave
  description: Anti-war content is spreading rapidly across social media platforms.
    Hashtag campaigns are reaching millions within hours, mobilizing people to gather
    in public spaces. The younger population is highlighting the economic and humanitarian
    costs of the war. This digital coordination is fueling the growth of street protests.
